https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/boundary-traversal-of-binary-tree/1

Approach:
If traversal is anti-clockwise
Right 3 methods.
1 to get the left boundary (Don't add leaf node)
2, To get all the leaf nodes
3. To get right boundary. (In this add the node in the temp list and then reverse the list and add it in final list) (Don't add leaf node)
